LanguageData.EggCaveSquiddleFertilized.label: cave squiddle egg (fert.)
LanguageData.EggCaveSquiddleFertilized.description: A fertilized cave squiddle egg. If all goes well, it should hatch into a baby cave squiddle. It can be eaten raw, but it's much better cooked.
